<varlistentry id="options.RubberBand">
	<term>RubberBand</term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Specifies the RubberBand type to use  when  moving  or  resizing
		non-opaque windows.  There are 3 styles:

		0: the window is represented as a number of rectangles
		1: one rectangle the size of the window
		2: one crossed-out rectangle the size of the window.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
